title: I Prevail - Hearts vs Mind (FLAC)
description:
Heart Vs. Mind is the debut extended play by American post-hardcore band, I Prevail. It was released on December 17, 2014. Music videos were made for the songs "Love, Lust, and Liars", "The Enemy", and "Crossroads".

Track List:

1. 	"Heart Vs. Mind" 	3:56
2. 	"Crossroads" 	3:29
3. 	"Love, Lust, and Liars" 	3:22
4. 	"Face Your Demons" 	3:11
5. 	"The Enemy" 	3:27
6. 	"My Heart I Surrender" 	3:27
7. 	"Deceivers" 	4:33


Blank space is not available on the first run of the EP, instead it was released as a stand-alone track and was later featured on Punk Goes Pop, Vol. 6.

Heart vs Mind Peaked on Billboards US Top Hard Rock Albums at 4th
